**Abstract**

We present a new method for the calculation of the \(\Delta\)-meson production in the \(\pi^{+}\pi^{-}\) final state. We show that the \(\Delta\)-meson production in the \(\pi^{+}\pi^{-}\) final state is dominated by the \(\pi^{+}\pi^{-}\) final state.
